snippet: Robert Karlsson and Kevin Stadler topped the O.H.L. Classic leader board at 12 under par when second-round play was suspended because of darkness in Mexico.
lead_paragraph: Robert Karlsson and Kevin Stadler topped the O.H.L. Classic leader board at 12 under par when second-round play was suspended because of darkness in Mexico.

headline.main: Darkness Halts O.H.L. Classic in Mexico
